  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Vasilis is a hand-drawn adventure game. The main character – Vasilis, lost her husband – Peter, in the rebellious city center. The city is in riots for a long time and almost everyday something burns or someone dies.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1002200/extras/0f2e33046774daa66a2163bfd47d715d.poster.avif?t=1728158697\" ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1002200/extras/0f2e33046774daa66a2163bfd47d715d.webm?t=1728158697\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The government left the center, which was dominated by local workers and students, who were able to build 4 towers that prevented people in the center from dying.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1002200/extras/21cd09ac7b935755e08d37838edfe01f.gif?t=1728158697\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1002200/extras/21cd09ac7b935755e08d37838edfe01f.poster.avif?t=1728158697\" class=\"bb_img\" /></picture></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Vasilis is a game focused on a character and a game plot, divided into 5 big chapters in which the player will dive into riots, cults, and cruel war events.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game was based on Ukrainian political events in 2014. </p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Vasilis is a hand-drawn adventure game. The main character – Vasilis, lost her husband – Peter, in the rebellious city center. The city is in riots for a long time and almost everyday something burns or someone dies.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1002200/extras/0f2e33046774daa66a2163bfd47d715d.poster.avif?t=1728158697\" ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1002200/extras/0f2e33046774daa66a2163bfd47d715d.webm?t=1728158697\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The government left the center, which was dominated by local workers and students, who were able to build 4 towers that prevented people in the center from dying.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1002200/extras/21cd09ac7b935755e08d37838edfe01f.gif?t=1728158697\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1002200/extras/21cd09ac7b935755e08d37838edfe01f.poster.avif?t=1728158697\" class=\"bb_img\" /></picture></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Vasilis is a game focused on a character and a game plot, divided into 5 big chapters in which the player will dive into riots, cults, and cruel war events.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game was based on Ukrainian political events in 2014. </p>",
